reviews.review_text:
The juiciest! This struck my ear as the juiciest of the sources currently up. Bertha is SMOKIN, and the bass sounds just fine to me...in fact the mix seems pretty much perfect (maybe the vocals are a tad back in some cases, but the guitars are crystal clear -- a fine trade-off once in a while as far as I'm concerned)

Two enthusiastic thumbs up!

Badass rhythm on truckin damn what an awesome truckin...not usually a favorite of mine...but damn...and jerry is like no where to be found...but bobby's rhythm tears is up...you hear the picks and fret slides so awesomely...because he is up too loud in the mix...lol...but it works for some songs...but others it is harsh
